{"tid":2280811,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好憎自己唔識做人","createTime":"2020-11-10T18:10:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T04:32:10.000Z","uid":366256,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91f1bb792e10b5a418c321e52f6f871e4a5b12ac","tid":2280811,"uid":366256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:10:51.000Z","msg":"成日人地心知肚明嘅是非/<br />\n邊個唔鍾意邊個/<br />\n邊個勊人憎/奇怪嘅人物關係<br />\n我未必係第一個發現 <br />\n但知道左之後好容易同人講<br />\n(明明人地同我一樣想法但冇明顯表過態)<br />\n我知道咁先係識做人 但成日控制唔到<br />\n明明成件事本來都係暗地裡 <br />\n好多人際關係問題大家都唔講<br />\n就俾我搞到浮左上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反而人地講到明係秘密我就唔會講<br />\n我覺得自己好唔識做人"},{"pid":"8de79c4d5572b4fe3aed6f09a12dd1246285f240","tid":2280811,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:23:26.000Z","msg":"得罪多幾次人你就會識"},{"pid":"9647569dd8f8128b785d845a7dae0cb8ffd20eac","tid":2280811,"uid":134103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:29:09.000Z","msg":"好過我，我多數係做俾大家憎嗰個<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要通常未俾人爆之前都以為自己好受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51dab788ed2e5565b495e64882b62cef25afb66d","tid":2280811,"uid":366256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8de79c4d5572b4fe3aed6f09a12dd1246285f240","tid":2280811,"uid":136186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:23:26.000Z","msg":"得罪多幾次人你就會識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T01:21:43.000Z","msg":"我都好驚其實自己得罪左唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f948dca4d4e260fa7b6eb6d4ac4ba0f3f0f545a","tid":2280811,"uid":366256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9647569dd8f8128b785d845a7dae0cb8ffd20eac","tid":2280811,"uid":134103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T18:2